---
import { siteConfig } from '../../data/siteConfig';
---

<section class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Image left - rounded with shadow -->
      <div class="reveal-scale relative">
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img
            src="/fotos-jd-infra/fotos jd infra/DJI_0004-1024x576.jpg.jpeg"
            alt="Bedrijfspand JD Infra drone"
            class="w-full aspect-[16/10] object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Floating stat badge -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 right-4 sm:right-8 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 hidden sm:block z-10 shadow-xl border border-secondary-100">
          <span class="block font-heading font-black text-4xl text-accent-400" data-counter="2006" data-counter-type="year">2006</span>
          <span class="text-secondary-400 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-heading mt-1 block">Opgericht</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content right -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-primary-500 leading-tight mb-6">
          Over <span class="text-accent-400">JD Infra</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-secondary-500 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          JD Infra aannemingsbedrijf is in 2006 opgericht en in de loop van de jaren uitgegroeid tot een vakkundig infrabedrijf met 12 tot 15 vaste medewerkers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary-500 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          In maart 2018 zijn wij verhuisd naar ons nieuwe bedrijfspand op industrieterrein Karreveld te Koudekerke. Van hieruit bedienen wij heel Zeeland.
        </p>

        <!-- Stats in rounded pills -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border border-secondary-100">
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-accent-400">18+</span>
            <span class="text-secondary-500 text-sm font-heading">Jaar ervaring</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border border-secondary-100">
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-accent-400">15+</span>
            <span class="text-secondary-500 text-sm font-heading">Vakmensen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-full px-5 py-2.5 flex items-center gap-2 border border-secondary-100">
            <span class="font-heading font-bold text-accent-400">100%</span>
            <span class="text-secondary-500 text-sm font-heading">Zeeland</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/over-ons/" class="group w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-accent-400 hover:bg-accent-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-heading font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Lees meer
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
